          <li><a href="https://www.ycombinator.com/" class="text-black hover:underline">Y Combinator</a> - Provides seed funding and mentorship for startups.</li>
          <li><a href="https://techcrunch.com/events/disrupt-sf-2023/" class="text-black hover:underline">TechCrunch Disrupt SF</a> - A startup event that includes pitch competitions and networking opportunities.</li>
          <li><a href="https://angel.co/" class="text-black hover:underline">AngelList</a> - A platform for startups to raise capital and recruit talent.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- E-commerce Startup Funding -->
