          <li><a href="https://www.kickstarter.com/" class="text-black hover:underline">Kickstarter</a> - A crowdfunding platform for creative projects, including e-commerce products.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.indiegogo.com/" class="text-black hover:underline">Indiegogo</a> - Another popular crowdfunding platform for innovative products and startups.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- E-health Startup Funding -->
      <div class="funding-category">
