          <li><a href="https://www.startuphealth.com/" class="text-black hover:underline">Startup Health</a> - A global health innovation company that invests in and supports health startups.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.healthcareangels.com/" class="text-black hover:underline">Healthcare Angels</a> - An angel investment network focused on healthcare startups.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

